      "section": [
        "Shoji"
      ],
      "text": "Shoji was a student at the Fire Nation school whom Aang met during his time there. He was like any other boy his age, and enjoyed playing with friends."
    },
    {
      "body": "Shoji was present when Aang first got in a confrontation with ${link_0} and was surprised when Hide did not fight Aang. He subsequently invited the ${link_1}, unaware of his true identity, to play a game of ${link_2} with him and his friends, which Aang accepted.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Hide",
          "key": "${link_0}",
          "target": {
