        }
      ],
      "section": [
        "Shoji",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "When the headmaster crashed the party with several guards in search of Aang, Shoji was the first to wear the belt of his uniform on his head, mimicking Aang's style, to help camouflage the young host. When the latter fled the scene, Shoji winked at him, though was shocked to see the tunnel through which Aang disappeared suddenly close due to earthbending."
    },
